Params: {1: 'Today I tried to venture into a new area that no one has set foot in before. If I can conquer it on my own, I think my ranking points will definitely go up a lot.', 2: 'ffffffff', 3: '2', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png', 6: '1'}
{1: "I failed this time, but it's okay. I still have plenty of time to try it.", 2: 'ffffffff', 3: '2', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png', 6: '1', 7: '2'}

{1: "Well, another day of failure in the challenge. But after these two unsuccessful attempts, I've managed to grasp the traits and movement patterns of the enemy.", 2: 'ffffffff', 3: '2', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png', 6: '1'}
{1: 'Next time, all I need to do is act according to the timeline.', 2: 'ffffffff', 3: '2', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png', 6: '1', 7: '2'}
{1: 'Whoever designed this test is so cunning! They even incorporated a dynamic ambush!', 2: 'ffffffff', 3: '2', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png', 6: '1'}

{1: "But it's okayâ€”I've already seen through all the tricks of the teachers. After I initiate the next assault, everything will be fine.", 2: 'ffffffff', 3: '2', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png', 6: '1', 7: '2', 8: '1'}
{1: "I couldn't beat the second phase... But seriously, why is there even a second phase?!!", 2: 'ffffffff', 3: '2', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png', 6: '1'}
{1: "Bieble, remember, you are aiming to earn the title of Chief. You can't keep losing like this.", 2: 'ffffffff', 3: '2', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png', 6: '1'}
{1: "Can't fail on the fourth try. Must win tomorrow!", 2: 'ffffffff', 3: '2', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png', 6: '1', 7: '2'}
{1: "I think I should take Freeman's advice.", 2: 'ffffffff', 3: '2', 4: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png', 6: '1'}
